Course Materials for my Calculus course that integrates history, computers, and the mighty calculus with Python.

<!--more-->

#### Course Description

These materials represent an introductory undergraduate Calculus class.  This course assumes little to no familiarity with Calculus, and aims to cover a basic introduction to the ideas of integration, differentiation, and differential equations.  My teaching philosophy aims to adapt a subset of the larger materials depending on the student audience and to leave substantial time for a culminating project based on student interest.

